{"tid":997861,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點同00後表弟講恒商當年有幾勁？","createTime":"2019-01-27T13:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T08:00:42.000Z","uid":121247,"like":66,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7318eb58dd411f5f22c3917d448e9d49952de226","tid":997861,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:23:41.000Z","msg":"早幾晚同親戚食團年飯，同枱嘅表弟今年入左中大係咁講中大金融有幾勁，我心諗恒管真係勁過多多聲。當年佢無論師資、校園、課程等等都一流；上年學校information day個才藝表演真係睇到我<br />\n個人同團隊榮譽都攞哂，最緊要係恒大真正比我知道乜係「快樂校園」，學生永遠都笑住讀書，係真正享受讀大學嘅趣味。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，以中大既聲望黎講，佢真係超班；但經歷過恒大管理學系的我絕對唔會覺得中大已經上左神枱。"},{"pid":"98ea2f944f3e89a06379993cf70e88b0802702bc","tid":997861,"uid":196924,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"咁你到底想講恆商恆管定係恆大勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3976563dd15a89e0e5b157c87269a1cc00c1693c","tid":997861,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,"quote":{"pid":"98ea2f944f3e89a06379993cf70e88b0802702bc","tid":997861,"uid":196924,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"咁你到底想講恆商恆管定係恆大勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:40:02.000Z","msg":"恒大既前身咪恒商囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed149180176d8c124ae4c029f7e639e0341aaf1","tid":997861,"uid":59832,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:45:13.000Z","msg":"pound of my school"},{"pid":"fca13de75e5b5eb424dd8d65423d79c32b7ca0bc","tid":997861,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3976563dd15a89e0e5b157c87269a1cc00c1693c","tid":997861,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,"quote":{"pid":"98ea2f944f3e89a06379993cf70e88b0802702bc","tid":997861,"uid":196924,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"咁你到底想講恆商恆管定係恆大勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h